<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="discuss-vt">discuss <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'skʌs/    美 /dɪ'skʌs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>讨论；商议：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>discuss sth with sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll discuss the problem with him later. 
稍后我将与他讨论这个问题。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>discuss + wh- 从句 / wh- to do：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We discussed how to do it and who should do it.
我们讨论了怎样做这件事和由谁做这件事。</p></div></div>